reviewText:
Uninspired work.
Run of the mill.
Best for only the super interested.
While it is very disturbing it is also informative as to the real threat of terrorism in the world today.
This disc was wrapped as new, however, there is a huge crack in it, making it unplayable. Please  advise. Thanks, Jeanne
Informative information on the terrorist group.  Not to endepth but still informative just the same.  Not for those that want a deep down biography of why they do the things that they do.
